but everybody is shifted down.

00:09:13.790 --> 00:09:15.364
All the physicians
are shifted down.

00:09:15.364 --> 00:09:17.030
And I think the
specialists are probably

00:09:17.030 --> 00:09:21.010
shifted down more in Europe
than the generalists are.

00:09:21.010 --> 00:09:22.930
We pay more for our
prescription drugs here.

00:09:22.930 --> 00:09:24.050
We pay more for--

00:09:24.050 --> 00:09:25.591
SALMAN KHAN: Now,
what are we getting

00:09:25.591 --> 00:09:27.716
in terms-- other than more
Mercedes in the doctors'

00:09:27.716 --> 00:09:28.257
parking lots.

00:09:28.257 --> 00:09:28.920
I'm kidding.

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:29.775
I'm kidding.

